<A>__{shot from her angle. she is sleeping beneath a chinese robe, on the chaise lounge. apparently she has changed her position, because the hand which is outside the robe moves. the camera, as though it were suzette, moves up towards grusinskaya. her eyes are closed. suzette crosses to the chaise lounge and is looking down. grusinskaya's eyes open suddenly. she looks at the ceiling and then her eyes turn and look straight at suzette.}
